textContent:
I don't want to be in a relationship that feels this way

And I am open to the idea of our relationship growing and am committed to this as long as we decide this is where we invest. 

I'm investing this time and energy here. I'm not putting these eggs in another basket. 

I have faith we can get to a different place but I don't know what that look likes and I'm committed to figuring it out together
